{"header":"<h1>Module type <code><span>Parameters.GENERIC_ELT</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"codex","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Union_Find","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Parameters","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"GENERIC_ELT","href":"#","kind":"module-type"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>A type for generic elements stored in our <a href=\"../../Functional/index.html\"><code>Functional</code></a> union-find structures. This should be a super-type of <a href=\"../../../../patricia-tree/PatriciaTree/module-type-HETEROGENEOUS_KEY/index.html\"><code>PatriciaTree.HETEROGENEOUS_KEY</code></a>.</p>","content":"<div class=\"odoc-include\"><details open=\"open\"><summary class=\"spec include\"><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">include</span> <a href=\"../module-type-SIMPLE_GENERIC_ELT/index.html\">SIMPLE_GENERIC_ELT</a></span></code></summary><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec type anchored\" id=\"type-t\"><a href=\"#type-t\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <span>'a t</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>The type of elements (nodes) in the union-find structure</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-polyeq\"><a href=\"#val-polyeq\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> polyeq : <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'a</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'b</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span>(<span class=\"type-var\">'a</span>, <span class=\"type-var\">'b</span>)</span> <a href=\"../../../../patricia-tree/PatriciaTree/index.html#type-cmp\">PatriciaTree.cmp</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>polymorphic equality on elements</p></div></div></details></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-to_int\"><a href=\"#val-to_int\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> to_int : <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'a</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> int</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Returns a unique integer identifier associated with the given element (eg hash-consed tag). See <a href=\"../../../../patricia-tree/PatriciaTree/module-type-HETEROGENEOUS_KEY/index.html#val-to_int\"><code>PatriciaTree.HETEROGENEOUS_KEY.to_int</code></a></p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec value anchored\" id=\"val-pretty\"><a href=\"#val-pretty\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">val</span> pretty : <span><span class=\"xref-unresolved\">Stdlib</span>.Format.formatter <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> <span><span><span class=\"type-var\">'a</span> <a href=\"#type-t\">t</a></span> <span class=\"arrow\">&#45;&gt;</span></span> unit</span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Pretty printer</p></div></div>"}